A dramatic cyberpunk cityscape at night where massive holographic data streams erupt like geysers from a single glowing node in the center, cascading upward into the neon-lit sky. The streams fragment into thousands of smaller light particles that spread across the urban horizon like digital fireworks. Buildings are covered in flickering screens and circuit-like patterns. The color palette features deep purples, electric blues, and hot pinks. In the foreground, a small rooftop garden with a single thriving plant sits beneath the spectacular display, representing the source point of this viral explosion of attention. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the chaos of light above.
